description: Van Gogh and artist Paul Gauguin penned the "exceptional" letter while living together in late 1888.
title: Van Gogh and Gauguin letter about brothel visit sells for 210,000 euros

maintext: "With Gauguin, blood and sex have the edge over ambition," he added. "But enough of that, you've seen him close at hand longer than I have, just wanted to tell you first impressions in a few words."
